Class SpaceObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.SwingConstants

    public class SpaceObject
extends javax.swing.JLabel
    The SpaceObject is an object in the Space. It has a Position, Rotation and a Scale that contains it's current state informations. It also has a Mesh that contains it's appearance informations that will be drawn on the ScenePaint.
    Author:
    John Konrad Ferraz Salomon - John´s Project
